ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-economic-growth-slipping-behind-texas-gdp-corporate-residents-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAffordability%20was%20another%20factor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20really%20were%20planning%20to%20move%20to%20Texas%2C%20but%20that%20obviously%20didn't%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Silverwood%20right%20away%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClair%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20had%20heard%20rumblings%20that%20a%20new%20development%20was%20coming%20to%20the%20high%20desert%20area%20about%2015%20minutes%20from%20where%20we%20currently%20live%20in%20Apple%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20scrolling%20on%20social%20media%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20a%20local%20news%20story%20about%20Silverwood's%20grand%20opening.%20We%20decided%20to%20go%20take%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20drove%20up%20the%20road%20to%20the%20property%2C%20we%20could%20see%20that%20they%20were%20paying%20great%20attention%20to%20details%20and%20aesthetics.%20The%20neighborhood%20looked%20open%20and%20clean%20with%20beautiful%20pools%20and%20hiking%20trails.%20We%20knew%20right%20away%20that%20Silverwood%20would%20be%20a%20really%20nice%20place%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClair%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20During%20our%20visit%20in%20April%2C%20we%20toured%2021%20available%20home%20models.%20But%20the%20minute%20we%20walked%20into%20the%20model%20we%20ended%20up%20buying%2C%20we%20just%20knew.%20We%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20our%20home%2C%20and%20that%20was%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downstairs%20has%20a%20great%20open%20floor%20plan.%20There's%20also%20a%20bedroom%20downstairs%20with%20a%20bathroom%2C%20so%20my%20mom%20doesn't%20have%20to%20go%20up%20and%20down%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20saw%20the%20kitchen%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20and%20just%20fell%20in%20love.%20