show%2F124738004.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20new%20autonomous%20fighter%20jet%20just%20broke%20cover.%20It's%20powered%20by%20the%20same%20AI%20brain%20that%20flew%20an%20F-16%20through%20a%20dogfight.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222443%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20large%20black%20aircraft%20sitting%20up%20on%20their%20tails%20outdoors%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f79d8a5dbc4fd10dab37b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShield%20AI%20is%20promising%20a%20fully%20autonomous%20fighter%20jet%20with%20its%20X-BAT.%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShield%20AI%20unveiled%20what%20it%20called%20a%20fully%20autonomous%20multirole%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20uses%20Hivemind%2C%20the%20AI%20pilot%20it%20previously%20used%20to%20pilot%20an%20F-16%20through%20a%20dogfight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20says%20the%20jet%20can%20take%20off%20without%20a%20runway%2C%20from%20container%20ships%20and%20remote%20islands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20that%20powered%20an%20F-16%20in%20a%20dogfight%20against%20a%20manned%20aircraft%20is%20powering%20a%20new%2C%20fully%20autonomous%20fighter%20jet%2C%20its%20maker%20said%20as%20it%20unveiled%20the%20new%20aircraft%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-ai-military-drones-shield-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20defense%20tech%20unicorn%20Shield%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20unveiled%20its%20new%20X-BAT%20fighter%20aircraft%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20company%20says%20that%20it%20can%20operate%20without%20human%20pilots%20and%20without%20runways.%20It%20said%20it%20can%20take%20off%20from%20islands%20and%20ships%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20warships%2C%20but%20also%20container%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmor%20Harris%2C%20Shield%20AI's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20aircraft%20engineering%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20brain%20for%20the%20new%20aircraft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-militarys-ai-fighter-jet-pilot-making-dramatic-advances-officer-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eis%20the%20company's%20Hivemind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20same%20combat-proven%20AI%20pilot%20we%20used%20to%20fly%20a%20modified%20F-16%20through%20a%20dogfight%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20a%20landmark%202024%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20during%20a%20testing%20exercise%2C%20the%20AI-driven%20X-62A%20Variable%20In-flight%20Simulation%20Test%20Aircraft%20(VISTA)%2C%20a%20modified%20F-16%2C%20went%20head-to-head%20with%20a%20crewed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-wont-say-who-won-real-dogfight-ai-human-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efighter%20aircraft%20in%20aerial%20combat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20military%20never%20said%20which%20aircraft%20emerged%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20simulations%2C%20the%20AI%20beat%20the%20human%20pilot%2C%20but%20this%20was%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20test%20involving%20aircraft%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20The%20then%20Air%20Force%20secretary%2C%20Frank%20Kendall%2C%20was%20riding%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20pilotless%20fighter%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowered%20by%20Hivemind%2C%20the%20new%20X-BAT%20can%20complete%20missions%20without%20human%20pilot%20involvement%20and%20can%20advance%20without%20GPS%20or%20reliable%20communications%2C%20Shield%20AI%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Artificial%20intelligence-enabled%20systems%20are%20considered%20necessary%20developments%20to%20break%20through%20contested%20areas%20that%20traditional%20crewed%20aircraft%20may%20be%20unable%20to%20navigate%20safely%2C%20or%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPilotless%20fighters%20are%20also%20not%20bound%20by%20the%20same%20design%20limitations%20meant%20to%20protect%20a%20human%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bunlike%20legacy%20crewed%20aircraft%2C%20X-BAT%20frees%20human%20aviators%20for%20missions%20that%20demand%20critical%20human%20judgment%20%E2%80%94%20an%20essential%20advantage%20in%20today's%20fast-moving%20and%20unpredictable%20conflict%20zones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20winged%20jet%20standing%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20jungle%20clearing%20with%20a%20mountain%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f799ca1c1f80efbec5f489%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShield%20AI%20said%20the%20X-BAT%20is%20designed%20to%20take%20off%20in%20remote%20locations.%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fc5713e-2880-4e6d-9069-7129ad79e90f%5C%22%3EA%20pilotless%20fighter%20aircraft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20that%20the%20X-BAT%20can%20also%20act%20as%20a%20drone%20wingman%2C%20working%20closely%20with%20crewed%20fighter%20jets%20to%20protect%20them%20and%20expand%20their%20overall%20combat%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVery%20interested%20in%20what%20autonomous%20uncrewed%20assets%20can%20bring%20to%20the%20force%2C%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20has%20been%20investing%20in%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%2C%20or%20CCAs%2C%20that%20can%20fly%20alongside%20crewed%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Increment%201%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20selected%20General%20Atomics%20Aeronautical%20Systems%20and%20Anduril%20Industries%20to%20develop%20two%20prototypes%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20received%20unique%20%26quot%3Bfighter%20drone%26quot%3B%20designations.%20Additional%20CCA%20designs%20are%20being%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20that%20the%20X-BAT%20was%20built%20for%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20comes%20after%26quot%3B%20the%20Increment%201%20development%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20this%20phase%20of%20the%20program%20has%20%26quot%3Bplayed%20a%20foundational%20role%2C%20and%20now%20X-BAT%20is%20pushing%20the%20envelope%20with%20advanced%20electronic%20warfare%20capabilities%2C%20greater%20payload%20capacity%2C%20and%20extended%20range%20that%20gives%20combatant%20commanders%20geographically%20distributed%20long-range%20fires%20and%20effects.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20an%20area%20that%20the%20military%20recognizes%20it%20needs%20to%20catch%20up%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20desire%20for%20CCAs%20is%20affordability.%20These%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20attritable%20warfighting%20platforms%20that%20can%20support%20and%2C%20if%20needed%2C%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20crewed%20fighters%2C%20which%20are%20more%20expensive%20and%20will%20ultimately%20be%20far%20fewer%20in%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%20said%20that%20the%20new%20X-BAT%20design%20%26quot%3Bdelivers%20high-end%20capability%20for%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20traditional%20fighter%20jets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilling%20the%20fleet%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20aircraft%20makes%20for%20a%20larger%2C%20more%20resilient%20fleet%20that%20can%20take%20hits%20without%20suffering%20severe%20pilot%20losses%20or%20budget-breaking%20plane%20losses%2C%20a%20necessity%20for%20high-intensity%20peer-level%20combat.%20Shield%20AI%20said%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20like%20these%20are%20%26quot%3Breshaping%20how%20future%20conflicts%20are%20fought%20and%20sustained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKendall%20said%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20AI%20competition%20is%20essentially%20going%20to%20determine%20who's%20the%20winner%20in%20the%20next%20battlefield.%26quot%3B%20And%20he%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20F-16%20dogfight%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20transformational%20moment%26quot%3B%20that%20marked%20the%20transition%20from%20when%20autonomous%20air-to-air%20combat%20was%20only%20%26quot%3Ba%20distant%20dream%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20emergence%20as%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20X-BAT%20was%20developed%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20keep%20pace%20on%20the%20battlefield%20amid%20rapid%20technological%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22839283af-5057-4789-9629-819f2a8bddce%5C%22%3EDeploying%20from%20anywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKey%20to%20the%20X-BAT%20design%20is%20its%20flexibility.%20Shield%20AI%20said%20it%20has%20vertical%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20with%20a%202%2C000-nautical-mile%20range%2C%20%26quot%3Bletting%20it%20launch%20from%20ships%2C%20islands%2C%20or%20austere%20forward%20sites%20without%20carriers%2C%20runways%2C%20or%20tankers.%26quot%3B%20That%20kind%20of%20range%20could%20prove%20valuable%20at%20overcoming%20the%20%26quot%3Btyranny%20of%20distance%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20vast%20Indo-Pacific%20amid%20a%20growing%20concern%20about%20conflict%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20wing%20with%20the%20Shield%20AI%20logo%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f79a9b5dbc4fd10dab3742%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShield%20AI%20says%20the%20design%20could%20be%20highly%20relevant%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20where%20land%20masses%20are%20separated%20by%20large%20bodies%20of%20water.%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%20said%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20platform%20in%20its%20class%26quot%3B%20to%20combine%20those%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig-deck%20amphibious%20warships%20could%20host%20up%20to%2060%20X-BATs%2C%20Harris%20said%2C%20but%20these%20aircraft%2C%20which%20have%20a%20small%20footprint%20and%20don't%20require%20a%20runway%2C%20could%20also%20be%20launched%20from%20atypical%20vessels%2C%20like%20a%20container%20ship%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20commanders%20the%20power%20to%20project%20combat%20airpower%20from%20almost%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20used%20by%20the%20US%20Navy%2C%20Air%20Force%2C%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20Army%2C%20or%20allied%20forces%2C%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20X-Bat%20was%20unveiled%20in%20front%20of%20military%20leaders%20and%20politicians%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20the%20X-BAT%20will%20be%20the%20future%20for%20US%20or%20allied%20militaries%2C%20but%20forces%20are%20increasingly%20interested%20in%20autonomy.%20European%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20giant%20Airbus%20has%20also%20tested%20its%20H145%20helicopter%20with%20Shield%20AI's%20Hivemind%2C%20which%20has%20also%20been%20used%20on%20a%20number%20of%20other%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshield-ai-new-aircraft-x-bat-autonomy-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761127202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f79234cc993f9955d08fdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshield-ai-new-aircraft-x-bat-autonomy-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shield%20AI%20says%20its%20new%20autonomous%20fighter%20jet%20could%20turn%20even%20a%20container%20ship%20into%20a%20launchpad%20for%20combat%20airpower.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshield-ai-new-aircraft-x-bat-autonomy-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cartier%20watches%20are%20having%20a%20moment%20with%20Gen%20Z%2C%20new%20pre-owned%20watch%20data%20shows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cartier%20watch%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7e16c1c1f80efbec60061%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223523%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECartier%20watches%20can%20go%20for%20well%20over%20%2410%2C000%20on%20t