3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cautious%20pace%20of%20announcements%20so%20far%20suggests%20that%20companies%20are%20not%20betting%20on%20a%20big%20seasonal%20surge%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm's%20senior%20vice%20president%2C%20Andy%20Challenger%2C%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20jobs%20site%20Indeed%20also%20shows%20that%20retail%20listings%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20October%20were%20lower%20than%20the%20same%20point%20in%20each%20of%20the%20prior%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20have%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-cut-seasonal-jobs-inflation-tight-labor-market-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslowed%20down%20in%20the%20seasonal%20hiring%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Indeed%20economist%20Cory%20Stahl%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEven%20of%20the%20postings%20that%20remain%2C%20we're%20seeing%20that%20they're%20not%20pushing%20as%20hard%20to%20get%20people%20into%20these%20jobs%20as%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20employers%20are%20slowing%20down%2C%20Stahl%20has%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-seasonal-hiring-job-searching-competitive-less-urgent-demand-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20people%20are%20looking%20for%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearches%20on%20Indeed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-christmas-decorator-owns-chicago-family-business-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseasonal%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20already%20well%20outpacing%20last%20year's%20rate%2C%20which%20was%20notably%20higher%20than%20prior%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Stahl's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20broader%20US%20labor%20market%20in%20a%20quasi-frozen%20state%2C%20seasonal%20jobs%20look%20increasingly%20like%20a%20lifeline%20for%20workers%20who%20are%20trying%2