%3D%5C%22e595c3ad-480c-411b-b317-82964bb103af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStart%20planning%20early%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20should%20consider%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20planning%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20how%20they'll%20handle%20their%20newfound%20assets%20%E2%80%94%20around%20the%20time%20they%20begin%20diligence%20on%20potential%20acquirers%20or%20even%20before.%20Why%3F%20%26quot%3BThe%20timeline%20of%20a%20delay%20could%20be%20derailed%20entirely%20by%20delays%20stemming%20from%20personal%20planning%20objectives%20missed%20in%20the%20early%20stages%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20should%20be%20upfront%20about%20their%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20selling%20price%20and%20ongoing%20ownership%20structures%20%E2%80%94%20and%20should%20be%20deliberate%20in%20selecting%20the%20right%20exit%20plan.%20A%20merger%3F%20A%20private%20sale%3F%20Sales%20and%20public%20offerings%20can%20convert%20years%20of%20illiquid%20equity%20into%20cash%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20sudden%20liquidity%20landslide%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20without%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20path%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20tax%20considerations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20level%20of%20control%2C%20cash%2C%20and%20future%20influence%20the%20founder%20will%20maintain.%20%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20entrepreneurs%20who%20very%20much%20want%20to%20maintain%20a%20sense%20of%20control%20as%20part%20of%20the%20exit%2C%26quot%3B%20Blum%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20entrepreneurs%20who%20have%20decided%20that%20maybe%20in%20their%20next%20phase%20they%20want%20to%20pass%20off%20some%20of%20the%20operational%20elements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223f2cb31-e4e6-4ca8-a314-c6914f7e1050%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20the%20right%20team%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAssembling%20a%20strong%20team%20well%20before%20a%20transaction%20closes%20can%20help%20crystallize%20such%20decisions%2C%20the%20bank%20s