fortune%20changed%20hands%20in%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20add%20a%20new%20block%20of%20transaction%20data%20to%20the%20ever-growing%20blockchain%20%E2%80%94%2012%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anton%20Peraire-Bueno%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7ae94cc993f9955d0944b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221195%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnton%20Peraire-Bueno%20(L)%3Cp%3EBI%2FJorge%20Castillo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2e79707-85a0-4cee-8de5-dc0e893922f4%5C%22%3ECurious%20Rabbit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnton%20Peraire-Bueno%2C%2025%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20his%20parents%20in%20the%20Boston%20area%2C%20also%20used%20an%20adorable%20screen%20name%2C%20as%20defense%20lawyers%20have%20repeatedly%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-fraud-trial-jury-picked-mit-brothers-peraire-bueno-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehighly%20educated%2C%20eight-woman%2C%20four-man%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Defense%20lawyers%20said%20%26quot%3BCurious%20Rabbit%26quot%3B%20at%20least%20five%20times%20during%20opening%20statements%2C%20as%20in%20%26quot%3BAnton%2C%20the%20Curious%20Rabbit%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAs%20you%20will%20find%20out%2C%20Curious%20Rabbit%20is%20really%20a%20perfect%20way%20to%20describe%20Anton.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%20Rabbit's%20curiosity%20is%20part%20of%20the%20case.%20Prosecutors%20have%20described%20a%20number%20of%20his%20Google%20searches%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20wash%20crypto.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20prison%20or%20jail%20worse%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20also%3A%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Estatue%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20limitations%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20defendants%20are%20graduates%20of%20MIT%2C%20where%20Snoopy%20was%20on%20the%20sail%20team%2C%20Curious%20Rabbit%20was%20a%20rower