tting%20crypto%20traders%20and%20make%20money%20for%20the%20traders%20who%20turn%20them%20loose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20smaller%20bots%20in%20the%20mempool%20get%20eaten%20by%20bigger%20bots%2C%20as%20happened%20here.%20We'll%20get%20to%20that%20in%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20photo%20shows%20a%20giant%20sandwich.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f26543cc993f9955d0662a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20%26quot%3Bsandwich%20bot%26quot%3B%20slips%20in%20a%20trade%20immediately%20before%20and%20after%20someone%20else's%20trade%2C%20kind%20of%20like%20the%20bread%20in%20a%20sandwich.%3Cp%3EScott%20Suchman%20for%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4bbf798-b46e-4cdc-9aa0-13dc36e0abc5%5C%22%3ESandwich%20bots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESandwich%20bots%20are%20a%20plague%20on%20everyday%20folks%20who%20just%20want%20to%20buy%20some%20crypto%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20Ethereum%20mempool%20is%20swarming%20with%20these%20little%20guys%2C%20according%20to%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20they%20work.%20Let's%20say%20one%20of%20these%20everyday%20folks%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BJoe%20Crypto%2C%26quot%3B%20we'll%20call%20him%20%E2%80%94%20risks%20a%20chunk%20of%20his%20life%20savings%20on%20a%20big%20cryptocurrency%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe's%20buy%20order%20gets%20kerplunked%20into%20the%20mempool%2C%20where%20it%20sits%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20waiting%20to%20be%20bundled%20into%20a%20block%20with%20other%20transactions%20and%20added%20to%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20the%20sandwich%20bots%20attack.%20In%20milliseconds%2C%20a%20bot%20places%20a%20trade%20immediately%20before%20and%20immediately%20after%20Joe's%20big%20juicy%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20surrounding%20it%20like%20the%20bread%20in%20a%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich%20bot's%20first%20piece%20of%20bread%3F%20That's%20a%20big%20buy%20order%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20for%20millions%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20crypto%20Joe%20is%20buying.%20The%20bot's%20buy%20order%20drives%20the%20price%20of%20Joe's%20trade%20up%2C%20meaning%20Joe%20will%20now%20pay%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20piece%20of%20bread%3F%20That's%20the%20bot%20selling%20everything%20it%20bought%20in%20that%20first%20slice%20of%20bread%2C%20but%20at%20that%20now-higher%20price%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20profit.%20The%20bot%20bought%20low%2C%20at%20the%20price%20Joe%20had%20hoped%20to%20pay%2C%20then%20sold%20high%2C%20all%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20crypto%20parlance%2C%20Joe%20Crypto%20is%20now%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20sandwich%20attack.%20He%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bsandwiched.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trial%20testimony%2C%20this%20is%20perfectly%20legal%20under%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain.%20No%20proprietary%20or%20private%20data%20has%20been%20breached.%20The%20bots%20merely%20took%20advantage%20of%20pending-transaction%20data%20that%20anyone%20can%20see%20by%20peering%20into%20the%20mempool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20takes%20us%20back%20to%20the%20Peraire-Buenos%2C%20and%20their%20big%20appetite%20for%20sandwich%20bots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sushi%20chef%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7b08b5dbc4fd10dab3ae1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOmakase%20is%20Japanese%20for%20let%20the%20chef%20decide%3Cp%3EMariah%20Tauger%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4db60f8-af98-431d-aa48-e78a2236e74f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20omakase%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peraire-Bueno%20brothers%20spent%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202023%20planning%2C%20coding%2C%20and%20running%20decoy%20trades%20with%20one%20goal%20in%20mind%3A%20outwit%20the%20sandwich%20bots%20and%20make%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20their%20multi-step%20plan%20the%20%26quot%3Bomakase%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20whether%20that%20strategy%20was%20fair%20play%20or%20fraud%20is%20the%20central%20question%20of%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20comes%20from%20the%20style%20of%20Japanese%20restaurant%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20chef%20sets%20the%20menu%2C%26quot%3B%20Katherine%20Trefz%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%2C%20told%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%20chefs%20%E2%80%94%20block%20%26quot%3Bvalidators%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20Ethereum%20parlance%20%E2%80%94%20are%20the%20Peraire-Buenos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20very%20simplified%20terms%2C%20the%20brothers%20set%20out%20some%20tempting%2C%20sandwich-meat%20bait%20in%20the%20mempool%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20bots%20to%20come.%20In%20milliseconds%2C%20three%20snapped%20at%20the%20bait%2C%20each%20building%20one%20of%20those%20buy-buy-sell%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20three%20sandwiches%20moved%20with%20lightning%20speed%20through%20the%20block-building%20process%2C%20the%20brothers'%20bigger%20bots%20attacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20the%20brothers%2C%20with%20their%20validator%20chef's%20hats%20firmly%20in%20place%2C%20were%20able%20to%20exploit%20a%20software%20glitch%20that%20let%20them%20type%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bpoisonous%2C%26quot%3B%20fraudulent%20row%20of%20zeros%20%E2%80%94%20the%20primary%20%26quot%3Bmisrepresentation%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20zeros%20gummed%20up%20the%20works%2C%20letting%20the%20brothers%20switch%20in%20three%20new%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich%20bots'%20initial%2C%20%2425%20million%20buy%20order%3F%20Those%20three%20bottom%20pieces%20of%20bread%3F%20That%20bread%20went%20straight%20into%20the%20Peraire-Buenos'%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmeat%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20sandwiches%3F%20Well%2C%20that%20cryptocurrency%20bait%20had%20always%20been%20in%20the%20brothers'%20control.%20Prosecutors%20say%20the%20brothers%20drained%20this%20crypto%20of%20its%20liquidity%2C%20turning%20it%20into%20%26quot%3Bshitcoins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20final%20top%20piece%20of%20bread%3F%20The%20sandwichers'%20%26quot%3Bsell%26quot%3B%20order%2C%20through%20which%20they'd%20hoped%20to%20gain%20a%20profit%3F%20That%20trade%20became%20invalid.%20It%20disappeared.%20These%20were%20open-faced%20sandwiches%2C%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cecc709-dbbf-463a-af25-f9021034f5b1%5C%22%3ELow%20Carb%20Crusader%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHungry%20yet%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20just%20one%20more%20food%20metaphor%20here%2C%20and%20we'll%20make%20it%20quick%20so%20we%20can%20all%20get%20something%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trial%20testimony%2C%20the%20omakase%20attack%20became%20public%20immediately%2C%20prompting%20a%20mix%20of%20criticism%20and%20hero%20worship%20in%20crypto%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20the%20Peraire-Buenos%20lobbied%20to%20clean%20up%20their%20image.%20They%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20Bert%20C.%20Miller%2C%20head%20of%20products%20and%20engineering%20at%20Flashbots%2C%20the%20company%20that%20had%20designed%20the%20otherwise%20highly%20regarded%20software%20that%20accidentally%20let%20the%20brothers%20type%20in%20and%20weaponize%20those%20%26quot%3Bpoisonous%26quot%3B%20zeros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiding%20their%20identities%2C%20the%20brothers%20noted%20in%20their%20email%20that%20they%20didn't%20like%20their%20negative%20press.%20From%20now%20on%2C%20they%20told%20Miller%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BLow%20carb%20crusaders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcheeky%26quot%3B%20reference%2C%20defense%20lawyer%20William%20Fick%2C%20who%20represents%20Anton%2