oklyn%20native%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20it%20from%20New%20York.%20The%20city%20is%20awash%20in%20seed%20checks%2C%20he%20says%2C%20but%20starved%20for%20growth%20capital%20to%20scale%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-consumer-tech-hub-startups-founders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20promising%20hometown%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlow%20has%20raised%20three%20opportunity%20funds%2C%20totaling%20%24295%20million%2C%20to%20join%20later%20rounds%20for%20its%20top%20performers.%20This%20gives%20Rechtman%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20backing%20breakouts%20rather%20than%20watching%20them%20migrate%20to%20out-of-town%20investment%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20takes%20off%20in%20New%20York%2C%20other%20people%20make%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Rechtman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20an%20opportunity%20to%20change%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amrussell%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emrussell%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40MeliaRussell.01.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20non-work%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoni-rechtman-slow-ventures-partner-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761123601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f802695dbc4fd10dab4859%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2