5-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20Web%20Services%2C%20these%20%26quot%3Bsolopreneurs%26quot%3B%20and%20bootstrapped%20startups%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bblind%20spot%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20customer%20discovery%20process%2C%20which%20heavily%20relies%20on%20connections%20with%20venture%20capital%20firms%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-q-lags-revenue-race-competitors-ai-coding-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAWS%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20several%20high-growth%20startups%20as%20early%20customers%2C%20including%20SurgeAI%20and%20Base44.%20SurgeAI%20grew%20to%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue%20without%20outside%20funding%2C%20while%20Base44%2C%20once%20solely%20owned%20by%20its%20founder%2C%20was%20acquired%20by%20Wix%20for%20%2480%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20blind%20spot%20poses%20increasing%20risk%20to%20cloud%20market%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20employees%20warned%20in%20the%20internal%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20became%20the%20dominant%20cloud%20provider%20by%20working%20with%20early%20startups.%20Some%20of%20these%20nascent%20businesses%20grew%20into%20huge%20tech%20companies%20that%20spent%20heavily%20on%20compute%2C%20which%20drove%20demand%20for%20Amazon%20Web%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20generative%20AI%20is%20messing%20with%20this%20successful%20formula.%20This%20new%20technology%20helps%20some%20startups%20get%20going%20with%20fewer%20employees.%20That%20means%20they%20sometimes%20need%20to%20raise%20less%20money.%20These%20smaller%2C%20often%20self-funded%2C%20businesses%20look%20from%20the%20outside%20like%20less%20interesting%20cloud%20customers%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20they%20may%20retain%20the%20ability%20to%20grow%20into%20substantial%20enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20challenge%20for%20AWS%2C%20which%20is%20seeing%20a%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%26quot%3B%20shift%20in%20how%20AI%20startups%20spend%20on%20cloud%20computing%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-startups-delaying-aws-spending-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20true%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20company%20is%20missing%20early%20signals%20of%20fast-growth%20startups%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20continues%20to%20%26quot%3Bengage%20founders%20as%20early%20as%20we%20can%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20VCs%2C%20via%20programs%20like%20AWS%20GenAI%20Accelerator%20and%20AWS%20Activate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22022ab7e8-8340-4d8e-ad8b-37086913d8b4%5C%22%3EBeing%20'out-hustled'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20the%20issue%2C%20AWS%20intends%20to%20adjust%20its%20VC-driven%20discovery%20approach%20to%20add%20a%20more%20data-driven%20prediction%20model%20designed%20to%20spot%20promising%20startups%20at%20an%20earlier%20stage%2C%20according%20to%20the%20internal%20Amazon%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20can't%20risk%20losing%20this%20market.%20A%20growing%20number%20of%20startups%20are%20run%20by%20a%20single%20employee%2C%20driven%20by%20AI's%20efficiency%20gains.%20Replit's%20CEO%20Amjad%20Masad%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freplit-ceo-vibe-coding-solo-startups-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20era%20of%20solo%20software%20creation%20has%20arrived%2C%20saying%20anyone%20can%20build%20an%20app%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20with%20the%20right%20AI%20prompt.%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Falexisohanian%2Fstatus%2F1752753792058294725%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-person%20billio