lity%20that%20manufactures%20gunpowder%2C%20explosives%2C%20and%20rocket%20fuel%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20salvo%20included%20air-launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstorm-shadow-missile-central-to-ukraine-counter-offensive-expert-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStorm%20Shadows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20subsonic%20cruise%20missiles%20jointly%20developed%20by%20France%20and%20the%20UK%20that%20can%20carry%20a%201%2C000-pound%20explosive%20payload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Defense%20Forces%20of%20Ukraine%20continue%20to%20strike%20strategic%20facilities%20of%20the%20military-industrial%20complex%20on%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20thereby%20weakening%20the%20offensive%20potential%20of%20the%20aggressor%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20said%20the%20results%20of%20the%20strikes%20were%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20assessed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defense%20ministry%20said%20it%20had%20destroyed%2057%20Ukrainian%20drones%20over%20Bryansk%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20but%20did%20not%20say%20if%20Storm%20Shadow%20missiles%20were%20detected%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryansk's%20governor%2C%20Alexander%20Bogomaz%2C%20also%20said%20that%20Kyiv%20had%20attacked%20the%20region%20with%20fixed-wing%20drones.%20While%20he%20later%20issued%20two%20missile%20alerts%2C%20Bogomaz%20also%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20Western-made%20cruise%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20and%20Ukrainian%20Telegram%20channels%20circulated%20clips%20of%20a%20large%20fire%20breaking%20out%20in%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20industrial%20facility%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20power%20substation%20in%20Bryansk%20had%20been%20hit.%20Business%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5